OL,7,FIt emerged during the trial that
OL,8,FWindsor was arrested but not
OL,9,Fprosecuted after sending a letter in
OL,10,FOctober 2020 to then-Scottish first
OL,11,Fminister Nicola Sturgeon which he said
OL,12,Fhad been "signed in blood" and which
OL,13,F"pledged his soul to Satan".
OL,15,FHe told jurors the letter was "just a
OL,16,Fjoke" and that he had sent parcels and
OL,17,Fletters to the radio presenters as a
OL,18,F"pretend weird" acting performance.
